Package: vivid
Type: Package
Title: Variable Importance and Variable Interaction Displays
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alan Inglis, Catherine Hurley, Andrew Parnell
Maintainer: Alan Inglis <alan.inglis@mu.ie>
Language: en-US
Description: A package for displaying variable importance and two-way variable interaction on the same plot. Can also display partial dependence plots laid out in a pairs plot style.
